  "detailed_description": "<h1>Discord</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >An unfortunate storymaker Jade, fallen into misery</h2></strong><br>Dana, a girl who presented a new day to Jade who was suffering day by day.<br>However, Dana surrenders and passes away due to the Sun's hatred that she brought Spring along with her.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109360/extras/4ab456e44404fed7bb4604251b4129fa.poster.avif?t=1693417145\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109360/extras/4ab456e44404fed7bb4604251b4129fa.webm?t=1693417145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109360/extras/4ab456e44404fed7bb4604251b4129fa.mp4?t=1693417145\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Will Jade ever be happy again?</h2></strong><br>Jade who's living a colorless life encounters a second spring like a miracle.<br>Will this little girl be able to bring happiness into Jade's life again?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109360/extras/6476e8f393aacfaef12a6d3766cc1656.poster.avif?t=1693417145\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109360/extras/6476e8f393aacfaef12a6d3766cc1656.webm?t=1693417145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109360/extras/6476e8f393aacfaef12a6d3766cc1656.mp4?t=1693417145\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >To those who are invited to the World of Black & White</h2></strong><br>You will become a character named 'Jade' and encounter the stories that are hidden in the the beautiful World of Black & White. Get ready to discover various stories and charcters and the grief hidden beneath them with Jade the old storymaker and a little girl.<br><br>You never know if you may reveal the false secret on the way. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109360/extras/a73de47f85e1b179cd47828eaf560607.avif?t=1693417145\" width=616 height=220 /></span><br><br><br>Welcome to Wonderland.<br>Enjoy the show :)",
